1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:08,000
1975-03-29 Science/Trigunatmika

2
00:00:42,088 --> 00:00:46,848
To you people I have told you many times by explaining adequately,

3
00:00:46,928 --> 00:01:07,188
displaying and by practically doing it.

4
00:01:07,268 --> 00:01:11,518
Prior to this I have said also that what Sahaja Yoga is,

5
00:01:11,598 --> 00:01:21,888
what happens in this, how it happens.

6
00:01:21,968 --> 00:01:31,808
I have given scientific explanations and scientific definitions sufficiently.

7
00:01:31,888 --> 00:01:35,888
However that which we call “science”.

8
00:01:35,968 --> 00:01:42,312
“Science” has not been created by man but they have searched and found it.

9
00:01:42,392 --> 00:01:47,326
They call it “science” but they have not created anything of the universe.

10
00:01:47,406 --> 00:01:50,540
No laws of the universe have been made by them.

11
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:56,420
No Shastra [science] had been made by them.

12
00:01:56,500 --> 00:02:00,860
Its laws and methods all that had been made by God.

13
00:02:00,940 --> 00:02:10,280
For example you see a circle and its diameter.

14
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:20,280
There is a ratio or proportion between the circumference

15
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:23,780
and its diameter that has not been made by you.

16
00:02:23,860 --> 00:02:28,760
Its law has been made by God only that it is neither more or less.

17
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:32,160
It will always be the same.

18
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,760
That ratio has been fixed.

19
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:41,360
All the laws and the regulations that have been made are by God only.Many

20
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:52,794
of you have asked Me, “Shri Mataji, why do you say 3 and ½ coil?

21
00:02:52,874 --> 00:02:55,319
Why 3+1/2 coils of Kundalini is said to be?”

22
00:02:55,399 --> 00:02:57,287
It is absolutely scientific thing.

23
00:02:57,367 --> 00:03:06,560
Those who might have seen the circle of a clock can understand this.

24
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:17,620
In the clock, the diameter D [Vyas 2R] of a circle and the circumference C [Paridhi

25
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:20,995
2ΠR=ΠD where R = radius of a circle],

26
00:03:21,075 --> 00:03:23,797
if diameter is 7 then circumference has to be 22.

27
00:03:23,877 --> 00:03:25,099
Neither less nor more.

28
00:03:25,179 --> 00:03:29,013
Their relationship is always 22/7 and it has been made as coefficient

29
00:03:29,093 --> 00:03:32,871
and its name is given as “pi” [Π] which means C/D=2ΠR/2R = Π = 22/7.

30
00:03:32,951 --> 00:03:36,880
If 7 become 8 then in the same proportion the circumference will be.

31
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:52,520
When this goes through the midpoint [of 3 ½ coils] then it has to become 7.

32
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:55,767
In the same way within us Sushumna Nadi has gone through.

33
00:03:55,847 --> 00:03:58,173
In that also 7 come.

34
00:03:58,253 --> 00:04:06,140
In that also 7 chakras [energy centres] are made.

35
00:04:06,220 --> 00:04:18,340
And in it also becomes [3+1/2] when you divide diameter [7] by 2.

36
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:26,155
If you make [3+1/2] coils, in that ratio of “pi” [Π],

37
00:04:26,235 --> 00:04:28,068
one over the other like Kundalini

38
00:04:28,148 --> 00:04:32,537
and draw a line through its central point then it well be divided into 7 parts.

39
00:04:32,617 --> 00:04:35,620
But is actually [3+1/2] coils only.

40
00:04:35,700 --> 00:04:45,860
Is there any scientist or mathematician here?

41
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:57,340
When you make coil one over the other and when you make hole through its centre

42
00:04:57,420 --> 00:05:08,844
point then it will cut at 7 places, therefore we have 7 chakras within us.

43
00:05:08,924 --> 00:05:11,424
But in case of circumference it is different.

44
00:05:11,504 --> 00:05:16,115
When you divide 22 by 2 then it is 11 and make half of 7 then it is 3.5 or [3+1/2].

45
00:05:16,195 --> 00:05:18,917
But you see how much mathematics are there in it.

46
00:05:18,997 --> 00:05:20,844
You can see it.

47
00:05:20,924 --> 00:05:23,536
That which goes through middle is as per seven.

48
00:05:23,616 --> 00:05:29,900
And that goes through the light is as per eleven.

49
00:05:29,980 --> 00:05:33,780
That is why when in our place we give money then we give 11 rupees.

50
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:37,980
Now you might have understood the importance of 11.Whatever is

51
00:05:38,060 --> 00:05:44,620
