55
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:01,564
But they had not been able to tell why it is so.

56
00:06:01,644 --> 00:06:04,256
But scientists may be able to say why it is so.

57
00:06:04,336 --> 00:06:11,300
When you wrap three and half like this then the whole circumference is covered.

58
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:13,480
Without that it cannot happen at all.

59
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:18,983
And when you make 7 holes from top to bottom the 7 chakras are made.

60
00:06:19,063 --> 00:06:21,785
Now scientists are searching this side [in modern

61
00:06:21,865 --> 00:06:24,643
