232
00:17:29,085 --> 00:17:33,752
It might be so and also might not be because a man’s mind runs according to his own,

233
00:17:33,832 --> 00:17:34,532
isn’t it?

234
00:17:34,612 --> 00:17:36,556
There was no necessity to touch it.

235
00:17:36,636 --> 00:17:39,914
After that in the temple its pujari [in charge of worship],

236
00:17:39,994 --> 00:17:41,883
all his chakras were badly caught.

237
00:17:41,963 --> 00:17:44,740
Chakras of all pujaris who were there were caught.

238
00:17:44,820 --> 00:17:49,432
On it sindoor [vermilion], donations, all those which had been offered were caught.

239
00:17:49,512 --> 00:17:53,956
One thing is naturally there in a man that it was an awakened and holy place but

240
00:17:54,036 --> 00:17:58,703
does not have that much sense that the vibrations coming from there is half of full.

241
00:17:58,783 --> 00:18:06,460
Three chakras of his [pujari’s] were also caught.

242
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:09,940
Even now I did not understand when I went

243
00:18:10,020 --> 00:18:13,420
inside the temple then pandit told Me that,

244
00:18:13,500 --> 00:18:16,900
“You cannot sit inside,

245
00:18:16,980 --> 00:18:20,380
you sit outside and you cannot touch it [statue of Ganapati].

246
00:18:20,460 --> 00:18:23,860
Then I thought that if I could not touch it

247
00:18:23,940 --> 00:18:27,340
then the statue will remain like as before.

248
00:18:27,420 --> 00:18:30,565
Then I went from behind and saw the statue

249
00:18:30,645 --> 00:18:33,089
and went near it and put My Sahasrara on it.

250
00:18:33,169 --> 00:18:36,280
Then vibrations gushed out strongly.Therefore it must be

251
00:18:36,360 --> 00:18:39,471
understood that you are the living instrument of Divine.

252
00:18:39,551 --> 00:18:43,829
If we say within you, more vibrations can come out compared to these temples.

253
00:18:43,909 --> 00:18:47,076
But first of all you must be living instrument of Divine.

254
00:18:47,156 --> 00:18:50,989
Those who like to have dead things, talk about dead things, they die.

255
00:18:51,069 --> 00:19:02,000
They become living dead.

256
00:19:02,080 --> 00:19:07,294
To run after dead objects [jada vastu] is a kind of hobby.

257
00:19:07,374 --> 00:19:10,652
To run after that or to run away from it is the same thing.

258
00:19:10,732 --> 00:19:14,287
To take to sanyasa [leave family life and go to Himalaya] and to

259
00:19:14,367 --> 00:19:17,923
run away from sanyasa, there is no difference between these two.

260
00:19:18,003 --> 00:19:20,058
You have to be firm on your position.

261
00:19:20,138 --> 00:19:22,694
First thing is you have to make your position.

262
00:19:22,774 --> 00:19:24,941
Second is you have to make your dharma.

263
00:19:25,021 --> 00:19:29,298
Dharma means you have to allow the flow of these vibrations out continuously.

264
00:19:29,378 --> 00:19:33,323
Sometimes you desire to go somewhere, you see somebody has fallen down.

265
00:19:33,403 --> 00:19:36,903
Then run and take hold of him and give vibrations and save him.

266
00:19:36,983 --> 00:19:38,483
Let the world say anything.

267
00:19:38,563 --> 00:19:41,674
Vibrations are flowing from you and that is your dharma.

268
00:19:41,754 --> 00:19:45,421
I have told you that the quality of gold is not that it is yellow.

269
00:19:45,501 --> 00:19:48,723
Its dharma is also not that ornaments can be made from it.

270
00:19:48,803 --> 00:19:52,581
Its dharma is only one and that it is never get spoiled by anything.

271
00:19:52,661 --> 00:19:56,216
Similarly diamond has its own dharma that it can cut everything.

272
00:19:56,296 --> 00:19:57,629
It is the hardest thing.

273
00:19:57,709 --> 00:20:00,265
In the same way the man has also his dharma to

274
00:20:00,345 --> 00:20:02,845
achieve God and know Him and those people who

275
00:20:02,925 --> 00:20:05,536
have achieved has their dharma to assimilate it

276
00:20:05,616 --> 00:20:08,061
completely and spread it all over the world.

277
00:20:08,141 --> 00:20:11,974
But when you talk this and that then you will not get either of them.

278
00:20:12,054 --> 00:20:19,100
Your vibrations will vanish and all My efforts will become of no use.There

279
00:20:19,180 --> 00:20:24,920
is no religion in the world where Divine vibrations have been told.

280
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:29,840
It means nobody has said so that vibrations are dharma.

281
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:32,961
They call it “Ruh”, “Water of Life”.

282
00:20:33,041 --> 00:20:36,819
They say anything but we say vibrations are real dharmas [religion].

283
00:20:36,899 --> 00:20:41,860
You have plainly known about it, how much it has been enunciated.

284
00:20:41,940 --> 00:20:45,103
Adi Shankaracharya has also praised it.

285
00:20:45,183 --> 00:20:47,572
It cannot be taught, written and explained.

286
00:20:47,652 --> 00:20:48,596
It has to happen.

287
00:20:48,676 --> 00:20:51,121
It does not happen to many intellectuals who

288
00:20:51,201 --> 00:20:53,645
think that they are well read and know more.

289
00:20:53,725 --> 00:20:56,947
To such great persons who are big stupids nothing happens.

290
00:20:57,027 --> 00:20:57,805
What can I do?

291
00:20:57,885 --> 00:21:01,240
It is an automatic happening.

292
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:04,460
It happens to many, happens to thousands.

293
00:21:04,540 --> 00:21:08,959
But if you stick to false and useless things and then you

294
00:21:09,039 --> 00:21:12,261
also talk about false things and you continue to catch and

295
00:21:12,341 --> 00:21:18,621
remain with false things which make you inert [immobile] then

296
00:21:18,701 --> 00:21:21,867
with that inertia [jadata] you will become stuck to that.

297
00:21:21,947 --> 00:21:26,392
The Chaitanya [living power] which is flowing from your person, you have to know

298
00:21:26,472 --> 00:21:38,360
how to spread it and for that you have to give some time, I have told you earlier.

299
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:42,723
It is true.

300
00:21:42,803 --> 00:21:47,006
But the ‘priority’ is also a thing.

301
00:21:47,086 --> 00:21:51,168
You have to change your priority.

302
00:21:51,248 --> 00:21:55,693
Within few days you will be established in your priority then you will enjoy it.

303
00:21:55,773 --> 00:21:59,605
You will get all the joy of the whole world.

304
00:21:59,685 --> 00:22:04,074
Whatever are the attractions and beauty of the world, all the wealth and Laxmi,

305
00:22:04,154 --> 00:22:08,654
whatever is there which you call knowledge, it is the source of all these things.

306
00:22:08,734 --> 00:22:14,416
It also knows, also loves and is the beauty too.

307
00:22:14,496 --> 00:22:20,412
It is the same Divine Power [Divya Shakti] about which we have read and known

308
00:22:20,492 --> 00:22:26,408
about it thousands times.And by this Divine Power the whole creation is created.

309
00:22:26,488 --> 00:22:32,404
You are created and by this only you will know it that it is the Shakti.

310
00:22:32,484 --> 00:22:38,320
This is a great thing.

311
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:41,676
Slowly and slowly it will shine.

312
00:22:41,756 --> 00:22:44,952
Any living process takes time and it grows slowly.

313
00:22:45,032 --> 00:22:48,228
It does not bear any quick process.

314
00:22:48,308 --> 00:22:51,504
But I see that its roots have gone very deep.

315
00:22:51,584 --> 00:22:53,694
Now I have come from Rahuri.

316
00:22:53,774 --> 00:22:58,274
I was very happy to know that the scientists there have proved it scientifically.

317
00:22:58,354 --> 00:23:03,021
They have done experiments on their plants and crops and made it a scientific thing.

318
00:23:03,101 --> 00:23:06,323
They were telling that they will go to government and tell

319
00:23:06,403 --> 00:23:09,792
the people about it [vibrations] that this is the only Truth.

320
00:23:09,872 --> 00:23:10,927
Rest it is untruth.

321
00:23:11,007 --> 00:23:13,780
We will tell everybody about its name [Kundalini]

322
00:23:13,860 --> 00:23:17,527
that his only is the Shakti which is your own.

323
00:23:17,607 --> 00:23:21,773
Your own shakti is becoming useless by the one which is sitting within you.

324
00:23:21,853 --> 00:23:26,120
For example in Yamuna river there were many pitchers

325
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:39,774
filled with water but when in those pitcher

326
00:23:39,854 --> 00:23:42,410
holes are made then the waters of pitchers mix

327
00:23:42,490 --> 00:23:44,990
with waters of Yamuna and become one with it.

328
00:23:45,070 --> 00:23:48,126
In the same way you should also become [like pitchers].

329
00:23:48,206 --> 00:23:51,317
But I want that you should know it fully and get it like

330
00:23:51,397 --> 00:23:54,786
Gopies and Gopes were searching in the times of Shri Krishna.

331
00:23:54,866 --> 00:23:57,421
That thing today you have got within yourself.

332
00:23:57,501 --> 00:24:01,668
I have told you many times that its depth [subtlety] is beyond microscopes.

333
00:24:01,748 --> 00:24:05,637
I have come to tell you the thing of that depth but become authorized.

334
00:24:05,717 --> 00:24:08,383
Those who have no authority, I cannot tell them.

335
00:24:08,463 --> 00:24:12,519
Therefore the thing I have told you today, I did not say earlier anytime.

336
00:24:12,599 --> 00:24:40,160
If anybody from you wants to ask any question then one or two persons may ask Me.

337
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:44,340
Please ask Me a question if anybody wants

338
00:24:44,420 --> 00:24:49,140
because I do not know what are your questions.

